description:
Once again I am bringing an old classic to to everyone. This is Zork I thru IV and Beyond Zork. All brought to you by GOG so it is DRM FREE. Included with the games are several fun items.

Just mount the image to a virtual drive and run the .exe file.

As per usual you will need a DOS emulator to play these games. Yes I suggest DOSbox ( believe it or not I do not work for them lol) 

You may find the latest version here:
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.dosbox.com/download.php?main=1&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.dosbox.com/download.php?main=1&lt;/a&gt;


I suggest you download and install DOSbox first then install this game.

Enjoy

NCHermit
